column1: # TITLE: Forest Inventory Data_Starksboro Town Forest

# SAMPLING LOCATIONS: Data collected from the Starksboro town forest in Vermont

# VARIABLE DESCRIPTION: Tree# indicates number of trees sampled within a variable radius plot sample; Species indicates the tree species sampled
column2: commen names are used the first letter corrisponds with the first word of the common name and the second letter is the second word of the common name; dbh stands for diameter at breast height
column3: tree quality is either Acceptable Growing stock (AGS) or Unacceptable growing stock (UGS)"
